description: RPS Consulting Pvt Ltd. is a leading enterprise education service provider in India, specializing in digital learning platforms and professional training programs. With 18 years of experience, they offer a variety of training methods including instructor-led, live virtual, and blended training across multiple domains. Their clientele includes international students and enterprise customers, with a focus on empowering professionals through certifications like Power BI and AWS Cloud Practitioner.
